{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Germans were standing-- actually, it was the Lithuanians who were standing right there and just threw them in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whoever was dead just fell in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And whoever was not dead, they would just push them into that grave and then put dirt around it, on top of it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were still hearing the cries of the, of the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So a few escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They just dug their way out of the graves and came back to Kovno.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- it was right--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was right within half an hour.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was the ninth fort.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to visit it, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a memorial right now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it was a, a fort-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at one time, it was built as a fort to, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to arm themselves against enemies, you know, and-- because Lithuania was always being invaded by one country to another.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so it was just a perfect spot for, you know, for silence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had lots of room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they dug the graves right there, the big hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many, many Jews were-- as well as Lithuanians from what I understand-- were killed right there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "May I add, also, that from what I, from what I remember is that the Lithuanians were even more cold-blooded murderers than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of the atrocities that went on, the Germans couldn't even bear looking at it whereas the Lithuanians were immediately with vengeance after the Jews, especially.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember them saying that Hitler opened our eyes up, that our eyes were closed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because most of the Jewish population in Lithuania, in Kovno, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were quite well off, and we lived quite a very good life.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
